title: Most Impressive Title?
description:
Domonique Foxworth, Israel Gutierrez and The Ringer's Kevin Clark debate if this is the Warriors’ most impressive championship and if the NBA Finals changed their perception of Jayson Tatum and Jaylen Brown.
